{"id":"index","title":"Index","type":"wiki","html":"<h1>Index</h1>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Master table of contents. Grouped by type, alphabetized within each group. Claude updates this on every ingest.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h2>🔫 The Trigger — ask your brain</h2>\n<pre><code>ba \"your question\"            # ask — interrogate past-you\nbc \"decision you're facing\"   # counsel — past-you argues both sides, anti-flattery\nbs                            # surprise — one unexpected connection\nbo \"topic\"                    # origin — when did this thread first appear?\nbx                            # contradict — past-you vs present-you\n</code></pre>\n<p>Phone trigger: drop a file in <code>raw/inbox/</code> with first line <code>? &lt;question&gt;</code> → answer appears in <code>wiki/queries/</code> within 3-5 min. Full setup in <code>bin/TRIGGER.md</code>.</p>\n<h2>Compounding Intelligence — what your brain has noticed</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Outputs from the trigger. These are the destination — not retrieval, not summary. Past-you talking to present-you and knowing things you don't remember.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>Generated by <code>brain ask</code></strong> (the trigger fires from here):</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"queries/2026-04-27-1950-what-was-i-writing-about-in-2022-2023-that-i-forgot\">the Té Amo plan you walked away from</a> — Dec 2023 operationally-specified founder-thread, partner named, pricing locked, then went dark</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Earlier autonomous-agent syntheses</strong> (proof of what the corpus can produce):</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"queries/contradiction-pricing-vs-broke\">contradiction pricing vs broke</a> — five money-voices in your head, $998/seat premium vs mad-at-yourself $5.50 horchata</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"queries/recurring-theme-you-havent-named\">recurring theme you havent named</a> — writing-as-feeling-exit, a 7-year unnamed pattern</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"queries/forgotten-thread-from-2022-2023\">forgotten thread from 2022 2023</a> — the COBOL ghost: 2023 idea, market actually arrived, you weren't there</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"queries/ahmad-jamal-to-rankett-throughline\">ahmad jamal to rankett throughline</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"queries/people-across-multiple-projects\">people across multiple projects</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Memory</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Memory</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Projects</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/rankett\">rankett</a> — primary venture, all-in bet (2026)</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"projects/brotein\">brotein</a> — pre-Rankett venture, fitness/protein app (mid-2025)</li>\n<li>— sibling ventures (names not yet captured)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Concepts</h2>\n<h3>Synthesis Pages</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/yahir-thesis-ai-search-2022-2026\">yahir thesis ai search 2022 2026</a> — four-year arc from \"asking the right question\" (2022) to Rankett's white-label AI search optimization GTM (2026)</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"synthesis/founder-loneliness-2022-2026\">founder loneliness 2022 2026</a> — the late-night second-person interrogations and the absent foxhole peer; the gratitude list and the 3am questions describe the same need from opposite directions</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"synthesis/family-as-hidden-runway\">family as hidden runway</a> — Mom and Dad as the actual safety net under the self-funded posture; no-runway-discipline is materially incomplete without naming the family backstop</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"synthesis/the-china-chapter-as-comparative-anthropology\">the china chapter as comparative anthropology</a> — six months in Shanghai as founder onboarding; markers-of-development + exclusivity-as-Chinese-trait + Alipay UX all flow into Rankett and BroMenu</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"synthesis/from-fitness-to-software-the-brotein-arc\">from fitness to software the brotein arc</a> — BroMenu → Brotein → Rankett as the same wedge applied to higher-margin surface area; fitness was a tactical wedge, not a passion</li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"synthesis/voluntary-adversity-as-philosophy\">voluntary adversity as philosophy</a> — seven-year thread from the 2019 \"fear of not doing\" axiom to the 2026 self-funded refusal-of-capital; the philosophy is <em>protection</em> against the comfortable self, not productivity ethic</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>All Concepts</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/60-day-activation-rule\">60 day activation rule</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/ai-search-optimization\">ai search optimization</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/ai-visibility-engine\">ai visibility engine</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/asking-the-right-question\">asking the right question</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/bridge-income-strategies\">bridge income strategies</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/china-chapter\">china chapter</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/covid-pandemic-era\">covid pandemic era</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/cyclical-time\">cyclical time</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/dad-wisdom\">dad wisdom</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/dao-mergers\">dao mergers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#\" class=\"mind-link\" data-node-id=\"concepts/disruption\">disruption</a></li>\n<li><a h